{"tid":1850142,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果下個月尾就係世界末日，你聽日仲返工？","createTime":"2020-01-29T11:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:27:08.000Z","uid":27718,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0a67895a06011065de1c808484fe9f5b097a2925","tid":1850142,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">醒未呀？</span></strong></span><br />\n平時睇電影，你班友就識笑鳩啲電影主角仲狗衝返工<br />\n而家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你自己咪又係衝去返工</strong></span></span><br />\n世界末日有好多種<br />\n喪屍、病毒、天災、人禍、核事故<br />\n電影演既野，已經係現實中發生緊<br />\n你仲擔心緊聽日無口罩點返工<br />\n咪撚返囉on9<br />\n打份工姐，你搵命博？<br />\n利申：同公司講左返唔到工，因為買唔到口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01998a487252654c3a7072ccce852528874d477b","tid":1850142,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:35:22.000Z","msg":"老閪都返工啦 唔返工邊有得無賞ot<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b46fe9b8b83864f7c3919d7cafc5f4e5fcf629","tid":1850142,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好悲哀，其實好多人  無左份工=不如去死"},{"pid":"2501ac3348ebae89c4a72481c66216fa86922556","tid":1850142,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"唔返工點見到女同事"},{"pid":"5b5a247358fa0d5393431f3b16fad3324a6bfa13","tid":1850142,"uid":64870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b46fe9b8b83864f7c3919d7cafc5f4e5fcf629","tid":1850142,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好悲哀，其實好多人  無左份工=不如去死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:15:28.000Z","msg":"係無咗錢=死先啱"},{"pid":"b05bfa1445552fb611992bef550f924ee0a1ef7f","tid":1850142,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":